# AI Instructions & Context

Always read `docs/AI_MAINTAINER_GUIDE.md` and check `.gemini/antigravity/brain/task.md` before performing any tasks.

## 🛡️ Core Rules
- **Keep Bot Lite**: Never add heavy plotting or bulky dependencies to the `bot/` package.
- **Modular UI**: Always extract new dashboard features into standalone components in `dashboard/components/`.
- **Transparency**: Update `task.md` and use `task_boundary` for complex multi-step work.
- **Data Resilience**: Ensure every new API route has error handling or fallbacks.
